window.bookSummaryJSON = "Scientists (and lovers) Mary Vaughan, who is human, and Ponter Boddit, who is Neanderthal, embark on the harrowing adventure of conceiving a child together. To overcome the genetic barbed wire of mismatched chromosomes, they must use banned technology obtainable only from a Neanderthal scientist living in the northern wilderness. <p>BONUS AUDIO: Author Robert J. Sawyer reveals the \"secret history\" of The Neanderthal Parallax trilogy.</p>"; 
